Package: ddir
Type: Package
Title: Assessment of the clinical DDI risk for drug compounds
Version: 0.9.2
Author: Rainer Strotmann
Maintainer: Rainer Strotmann <rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org>
Description: The goal of ddir is to facilitate the analysis of the drug-drug
